simplelist.member:
- the its:versionattribute from the
                    namespace http://www.w3.org/2005/11/its,
                        optional.

note.para:
Please note that this specification does not define explicit markup for inline directional Overrides or Embeddings;
      in case those are needed. Extractors and Modifiers will need
      to use [UAX #9] defined Directional Formatting Characters.
